############################################################################
# FvwmButtons
#

Colorset 8 fg white, bg #888888, fgsh black, RootTransparent Buffer, Tint #000000 50
Style FvwmButtons NoTitle, StaysOnBottom, Sticky, WindowListSkip, CirculateSkipIcon, CirculateSkip
Style FvwmButtons HandleWidth 2, NeverFocus, Layer 1

*FvwmButtons: Colorset 8
*FvwmButtonsFont -adobe-helvetica-bold-r-*-*-18-*-*-*-*-*-*-*
*FvwmButtonsGeometry 864x36+0-0
*FvwmButtons: Rows 1
*FvwmButtons: Columns 12

*FvwmButtons (Size 1x1, Title "Restart", Icon $[fvwm_icon]/fvwm.png,	Restart)
*FvwmButtons (Size 22x1, Terminal	$[fvwm_icon]/term.png	Exec "xterm" $[fvwm_term] &)
*FvwmButtons (Size 22x1, Emacs	$[fvwm_icon]/emacs.png	Exec "Emacs" emacs -geometry =80x78-0+0 &)
*FvwmButtons (Size 22x1, Browser	$[fvwm_icon]/firefox.png	Exec "Browser" $[fvwm_browser])
*FvwmButtons(Size 22x1, Swallow XBiff 'Exec xbiff &')
*FvwmButtons(Size 22x1,Swallow(UseOld,NoKill) "xload" \
	`Exec xload -title xload -bg SteelBlue3 -update 3 -nolabel &`)
*FvwmButtons(Size 22x1,Swallow XEyes 'Exec xeyes -center LightGrey &')
*FvwmButtons(Size 36x1,Swallow XClock 'Exec xclock -d -twentyfour -fg white -bg SteelBlue3 &')
*FvwmButtons(Size 26x1,Swallow "FvwmPager" "FvwmPager 0 0")
*FvwmButtons: (Size 16x1 Lock Screen	Exec exec xscreensaver-command --lock)


